Revision history for Perl extension Brownie

0.09
        - use Selenium::Server, instead of Align::SeleniumRC (ikasam_a)
        - experimental Brownie::DSL (Cside)
        - can use external selenium server permanently (Cside)

0.08
        - support Selenium RemoteWebDriver (selenium-server) driver
        - fixed syntax error on Session.pm

0.07
        - added missing dependency

0.06
        - remove Selenium (Remote / Selenium-Server) driver
        - support Mechanize driver
        - support local app w/ Plack::Runner

0.05
        - does not call clear() if file attachment field
        - support input[not(@type)] as text field

0.04
        - added status_code() and response_headers() to driver I/F
        - tests based on shared examples

0.03
        - refresh current_node every time

0.02
        - add eg/google.pl
        - joining XPath
        - use selenium driver native find_element()

0.01
        - original version
        - implements selenium driver
